This page provides a timeline of key events related to immigration enforcement in the {{w|United Kingdom}}. The focus is on enforcement activities such as those carried out by {{w|Immigration Enforcement}}, detention operations, and border patrol carried out by the {{w|Border Force}}. Changes to visa policy or nationality policy are not included, except insofar as they very directly tie in with enforcement.

